{"tid":1973734,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"法療養院「冇口罩但有屍袋」　護士：政府認為老人已活夠了","createTime":"2020-04-15T11:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T11:12:32.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d43eeaa72fb89e003e39c28e18f66ee2caca4bb7","tid":1973734,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/4/1586945772_8M-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F4%2F1586945772_8M-1280w.jpg&h=32798257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎持續於歐洲肆虐，老人家成為高危一族，但在防疫物資短缺下，他們成為了被遺忘的一群。<br />\n<br />\n法國《世界報》(Le Monde)的記者到塞納-聖但尼省(Seine-Saint-Denis)一間療養院採訪，該院數日前已經暫停所有額外活動，加上3月11日起，政府為阻止病毒擴散而下令療養院禁止所有外人探訪，包括家人，長者們只能透過窗戶，呆看街上的人來人往。<br />\n<br />\n從某天開始，連路上的人車也消失了，輔導員向長者們解釋：「政府下令全國人民都要待在家裡，不可出門。」數天後，老人家在實施新措施下，不能聚在一起用餐，只能各自孤獨地於房間內吃飯，一名婆婆看來因此失去食慾，她把叉子放下，並向醫護人員哀嘆：「我該怎麼辦？」<br />\n<br />\n雖然政府指流行病已進入第三階段，醫療院所的人必須戴上口罩，但療養院內沒人有口罩&mdash;&mdash;院方在3月初訂了口罩，但廠方後來告知，全部口罩已被政府徵收；向政府提出要求，回覆是「正在處理」。療養院一名護士坦言：「我知道政府在想甚麼，『那邊的都是老人，他們已經活夠了』。」<br />\n<br />\n除了口罩，療養院的消毒酒精及手套都用完了。院長波諾(Edouard Prono)收到衛生部的指示：最初療養院必備的口罩，現在如非確診，就不是必要的了。主任賈西亞(Laurent Garcia)嘆道：「口罩沒有，但有屍袋。你明白這個訊息嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n幾天後，療養院有3名工作人員出現病徵，當中2人確診新冠肺炎。院內士氣低沉，一名護理師表示：「現在每分鐘都變成戰爭，我已看不到前路。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%b3%95%e7%99%82%e9%a4%8a%e9%99%a2%e3%80%8c%e5%86%87%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9%e4%bd%86%e6%9c%89%e5%b1%8d%e8%a2%8b%e3%80%8d%e3%80%80%e8%ad%b7%e5%a3%ab%ef%bc%9a%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e8%aa%8d%e7%82%ba%e8%80%81%e4%ba%ba%e5%b7%b2%e6%b4%bb%e5%a4%a0%e4%ba%86-215190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b3%2595%25e7%2599%2582%25e9%25a4%258a%25e9%2599%25a2%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2586%2587%25e5%258f%25a3%25e7%25bd%25a9%25e4%25bd%2586%25e6%259c%2589%25e5%25b1%258d%25e8%25a2%258b%25e3%2580%258d%25e3%2580%2580%25e8%25ad%25b7%25e5%25a3%25ab%25ef%25bc%259a%25e6%2594%25bf%25e5%25ba%259c%25e8%25aa%258d%25e7%2582%25ba%25e8%2580%2581%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25b7%25b2%25e6%25b4%25bb%25e5%25a4%25a0%25e4%25ba%2586-215190&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQP3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=6fa6fa64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e6%b3%95%e7%99%82%e9%a4%8a%e9%99%a2%e3%80%8c%e5%86%87%e5%8f%a3%e7%bd%a9%e4%bd%86%e6%9c%89%e5%b1%8d%e8%a2%8b%e3%80%8d%e3%80%80%e8%ad%b7%e5%a3%ab%ef%bc%9a%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e8%aa%8d%e7%82%ba%e8%80%81%e4%ba%ba%e5%b7%b2%e6%b4%bb%e5%a4%a0%e4%ba%86-215190</a>"},{"pid":"853daad9e0a5d40ea163e351d26467348ce36844","tid":1973734,"uid":102681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:08:11.000Z","msg":"我估到會有好多左膠喊慘，但要揀都一定係咁揀"},{"pid":"39f9f3c0893b528e75dabd635a8eff5b3fe7b648","tid":1973734,"uid":229185,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:09:30.000Z","msg":"唔係咁架， 歐洲咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你呢啲係fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1acf42cf248dd3592fef6b531a25456665cd316","tid":1973734,"uid":272922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"39f9f3c0893b528e75dabd635a8eff5b3fe7b648","tid":1973734,"uid":229185,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:09:30.000Z","msg":"唔係咁架， 歐洲咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk